<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Sattelpog<ex>er</ex></expan>, als wir ewch vormals wie oft
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und gemant
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>laiste<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        Perching nach <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>schuldbr<ex>iefs</ex></expan> sag, den wir von
                                <expan>Hilpolte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daran ir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> bürg
                        seyt, daz aber ir bisher <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> und niht getan
                        habt, des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> niht getrawt
                            <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>. Also manen wir ewch
                                <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> mit disem
                            <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>, daz ir noch
                                <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> knecht mit <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        pferd schikt gen Perching in <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Windisch hawse,
                        der da laiste von pferden zu <expan>pferd<ex>en</ex></expan>, und ausz der
                                <expan>laistu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> niht <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        nach <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>schuldbr<ex>iefs</ex></expan> sag, bis wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> schulde beczalt
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Und getrawn
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>, ir sehet ewrselbs
                                <expan>gelimpf<ex>en</ex></expan> an und
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czieht</expan> uns des niht
                            <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan>, wan uns niht lieb
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e,</expan> daz wir uns des von ewch
                                <expan>beklage<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>sölte<ex>n.</ex></expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Udalrici. </ab>
</div>
